uantify the upstream Scope 3 emissions or provide specific figures.\"\n}\n```", "24": "```json\n{\n  \"upstream_scope_3_targets\": [\"90% of our key suppliers* to disclose their environmental targets and actions by the end of 2025\"], \n  \"reasoning\": \"The report explicitly mentions 'As part of our goal to reach net-zero by the end of 2025, we set an ambitious target requiring 90% of our key suppliers* to disclose their environmental targets and actions being taken to reduce emissions by the end of 2025.'\"\n}\n```", "25": "```json\n{\n  \"scope_3_emissions\": \"none\",\n  \"reasoning\": \"The sustainability report does not explicitly mention a specific downstream Scope 3 emissions number for the year. Instead, it discusses efforts to engage suppliers in disclosing their emissions reduction targets and actions, but does not present a quantified Scope 3 emissions figure.\"\n}\n```", "26": "```json\n{\n  \"scope_3_targets\": [\"90% of key suppliers to disclose environmental targets and actions by 2025\"],\n  \"reasoning\": \"The report explicitly states that 'As part of our goal to reach net-zero by the end of 2025, we set an ambitious target requiring 90% of our key suppliers* to disclose their environmental targets and actions being taken to reduce emissions.'\"\n}\n```", "27": "```json\n{\n  \"climate_contributions\": [\"$1.6M+ spent on skills to succeed initiatives to equip people with skills to make substantive improvements to their lives since 2009\", \"Invested in nature-based carbon removals expected to remove an estimated 13 million+ metric tons of carbon over the next 20 years\", \"Planted 674,000 trees representing one tree for each person at Accenture at the time of the announcement in December 2021\"],\n  \"reasoning\": \"The report details contributions such as the $1.6M+ spent on skills to succeed initiatives, investments in nature-based carbon removals, and the planting of 674,000 trees, all aimed at reducing emissions and supporting sustainable practices.\"\n}\n```", "28": "```json\n{\n  \"offsetting_claims\": [\n    \"Invested in nature-based carbon removals expected to remove an estimated 13 million+ metric tons of carbon over the next 20 years.\",\n    \"97% renewable electricity toward our goal of 100% by the end of 2023.\"\n  ],\n  \"reasoning\": \"These claims are justified in the report under 'Path to net-zero' and 'Renewable electricity' sections, detailing the progress and targets related to carbon removal and renewable energy.\"\n}\n```", "29": "```json\n{\n  \"targets_info\": [\n    \"Reduce absolute greenhouse gas emissions by 11% from 2016 baseline (achieved 68% reduction by FY22, surpassing target)\",\n    \"Achieve 100% renewable electricity in offices by end of 2023 (reached 97% in FY22)\",\n    \"Achieve net-zero emissions by end of 2025\",\n    \"Reuse or recycle 100% of e-waste, including office furniture, by end of 2025 (reached 99% for computers and workstations in FY22)\",\n    \"Ensure 90% of key suppliers disclose environmental targets and actions to reduce emissions by end of 2025 (68% disclosed targets, 75% disclosed actions as of FY22)\",\n    \"Invest in nature-based carbon removals expected to remove 13 million+ metric tons of carbon over next 20 years\",\n    \"Achieve gender parity by 2025 (women now represent 47% of workforce, 29% of managing directors)\"\n  ],\n  \"reasoning\": \"Targets are outlined in", "30": "```json\n{\n  \"targets_summary\": \"Accenture aims to achieve net-zero emissions by the end of 2025, with 97% renewable electricity by 2023, and 90% of key suppliers disclosing environmental targets and actions by 2025.\",\n  \"reasoning\": \"This summary is derived from the report's detailed descriptions of their environmental targets, including the Science-Based Target initiative, the UNGC Business Ambition for 1.5\u00b0 Pledge, and the commitment to reach net-zero emissions by 2025. The report also mentions that 97% of their electricity is renewable by the end of 2